            <div class="J_Content" data-emote="0">
                <!---doc_text---><p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#333333;font-family:新宋体;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#333333;font-family:新宋体;">南浔素有“鱼米之乡”、“丝绸之府”之美誉。浓厚的江南水乡风貌，古朴的民俗风情名闻遐迩；绵远深厚的文化底蕴，藏书文化独步华夏；欧陆情调与江南古风并处，中西合璧的宏屋巨宅瑰玮奇绝，韵动中外。南浔，更有自近代以来开明、开放、开拓的独特人文精神，以及与此一脉相承的充满创造和活力的当代发展风范。<span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>南浔是“文化之邦”、“院士之乡”。早在明代，南浔镇就有“九里三阁老，十里两尚书”之说。仅宋、明、清三代，就有进士<span>42</span>名。近现代南浔名人群体崛起的现象更为世人所瞩目，如辛亥革命先驱张静江、体育家徐一冰、杭州西泠印社发起人之一的文物鉴赏家张石铭、著名作家徐迟、中国导弹驱逐舰之父潘镜芙、中国航天之父屠守锷、新中国飞机设计第一人徐舜寿、北京大学校长张龙翔、“燕京大学”校长陆志韦、“中山大学”首任校长和“中央大学”首任校长张乃燕等。今天，南浔籍的两院院士仍有<span>8</span>名之多。<span></span></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．　董份</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1510--1595) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字用均，一字体化，号浔阳山人，环子。明乌程</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">今湖州</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">南浔镇人。嘉靖十六年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1537)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">举人，二十年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1541)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">进士。授翰林院编修，参与纂修会典，转右春坊，右中元，管国子司业事。明世宗朱厚熄</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1522—1566)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">斋居西宫时，亲点其出任翰林学士，不久加太常少卿，赐一品服。继晋升礼部右侍郎，赐飞鱼服，支从一品俸。旋转任吏部左侍郎，兼翰林学土，掌詹事府事，会修《承天大志》，为副总裁。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　董份曾于嘉靖二十三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1544)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">及三十二年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1553)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">两次出任会试同考官。三十五年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1556)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">参与典武会试，三十七年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1558)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">主试北闱，次年充会试同考，总裁南官，为朝庭举荐人才有功，故于嘉靖四十一年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1562)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">赐蟒服及</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">东观总裁</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">印章，加工部尚书。仍兼吏部侍郎，继举升礼部尚书兼翰林学士。后为给事中欧阳一敬举劾，遭削职为民，回归故里，收族人，创义田，筑义宅，办义宅和义仓。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　董份在通津桥</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">俗名大桥</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">北堍有大住宅，称</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">大宗伯第</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。前临东大街，后沿栲栳湾，东起德懋弄，西至宝善街，内有</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">爱莲池</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，有小溪通栲栳湾，原称</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">藕河头</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，俗名</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">后河头</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。东大街大门对河，原有大罩墙，名</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">看墙头</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，东侧有</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">看墙弄</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之名，今改名</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">船场滨弄</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。晚年因利用荒年，贱价购买乡民土地，收租放高利贷，放纵家仆，欺诈暴征，激起民愤，农民围宅鼓噪，又遭谏官参奏，致忧郁成疾。万历二十三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1595)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">病卒，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">86</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁，遗嘱</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">毋书吾故宫，以白布三尺题曰耐辱主人足矣</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。著述有《史记评钞》四十卷，《汉书评钞》四十卷，《后汉书评钞》二十卷，序《万历湖州府志》十卷，及《泌园集》三十七卷等。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．沈淮</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(?</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">一</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">1623) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字铭镇，乌程南浔马腰人。明神宗万历二十年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1592)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">进士，万历末年，大学士方从哲专权，为植私党，以乡谊关系，推荐为阁员。光宗朱常洛泰昌元年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1620)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">秋八月即位，召沈为礼部尚书兼东阁大学士。沈官翰林时，尝授内侍书，魏忠贤、刘朝皆其弟子。既人阁，密结二人，朋比为奸，取得熹宗朱由校信任和重用。不久，加太子太保，进文渊阁，再进授少保兼太子太保，户部尚书，武英殿大学士等职。沈为扩张个人权势，结党营私，打击异已，独揽朝政，激起诸大臣忿恨不满。天启二年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1622)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">三月，给事中惠世扬、周朝瑞、御史江秉谦等劾沈勾结阉党魏忠贤、刘朝弄兵内宫，图谋不轨，但未获结果。五月，刑部尚书王纪再劾沈，言其劣迹比之蔡京，而沈亦谧劾王纪，针锋相对。未几，王纪削职去，而沈则掌权如故。群臣议论不平，互相攻讦，叶向高乃向熹宗进言，认为王纪与沈淮均为朝中大臣，互相攻讦，有失体统，今独斥王纪而宽沈，似不得公论。熹宗心有所动，沈自感不安，乃引退归里。天启三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1623)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">病卒，谥文定。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> <br>
</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　按《冷卢杂识》评曰：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">朱文肃公</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">朱国祯</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">倡均徭之议，东南大水，又请改折，德泽及人，乡邦推重。沈结纳客魏、温体仁奸私误国，闾里羞称之。三人皆载《明史》，而府县志列传独详文肃事实，沈</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">淮</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">、温</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">体仁</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">则讳而不书。逞志一时，陨名千载，呜呼</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">!</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">此亦足以为鉴戒也</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">3</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．朱国祯</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1558--1632) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">明乌程南浔人。字文宇，号平涵，又号叫庵居士、守愚子。故居在马家港河东原高等小学后面。明万历十六年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1588)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">举人，十七年进士，累官国子监祭酒，右春坊等职，谢病不出。天启元年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1621)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">提升礼部右侍郎，中途请告归，未上任。天启三年拜礼部尚书兼东阁大学士，后改文渊阁大学士，累加少保兼太子太保。四年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1624)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">春晋户部尚书，武英殿大学士，总裁《国史实录》，不久加少傅兼太子太保。时魏忠贤窃权，朱国祯为叶向高首辅助手，向高去职，由韩火广继之；韩火广又罢官，朱国祯任首辅。旋为魏党李蕃所劾，朱国祯连上三疏，引疾归里。魏忠贤谓其党曰：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">此老亦邪人，但不作恶，可令善去。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">乃加少师兼太子太师，晋吏部尚书兼建极殿大学士，遣人送归故里。崇祯五年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1632)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卒，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">76</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁，赠太傅，谥文肃。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　朱国祯处逆境时，独能不阿，洁身引退。性直率坦，虽位至辅相而家业萧然。其南浔旧居原在马家港河东，窄小犹如普通人家。朱国祯居官能关心家乡民情，创议均田均役。他写信给巡抚说明赋役不平之弊，应计亩定役，贫民得苏。万历三十六年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1608)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。湖苏大水成灾，荻塘塌损，田禾全没，朱国祯致书巡抚，力请救荒，重修荻塘</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">一名东塘</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。湖州知府陈幼学洞察民隐，同心区划，荻塘大修，朱国祯撰《修东塘记》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">文见刘祈春《乌程县志》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　朱国祯告老归田后，留心典故，潜心著作，有《明史概》一百四十二卷，《皇明纪传》三十卷，《大政记》三十六卷，《涌幢小品》三十二卷</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">其名所出，盖朱国祯尝构木为亭，六角如石幢，结构略如穹庐，可以择地而移，随意而张，忽如涌出，故以为名。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，《四库全书总目提要》给予良好评价，认为：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">其是非不甚失真，在明季说部之中，．尤为质实</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。此外尚有《朱文肃遗集》八册，《平涵诗文钞》二册。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．温体仁</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1573—1639) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字长卿，乌程南浔辑里村人。明万历二十五年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1597)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">举人，时年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">16</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，补博士弟子员。二十六年中进士，二十八年授翰林院编修，四十四年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1616)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">升少詹事，掌南京翰林院印。天启二年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1622)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">升礼部右侍郎，协理詹事，次年回部任左侍部。七年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1627)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">晋南京礼部尚书。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　崇祯三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1630)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">任礼部尚书兼东阁大学士，加太子太保，进文渊阁，五年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1632)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">加少保兼太子太保，户部尚书，进武英殿。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　温体仁既人阁，势力益扩张，阴结党羽，陷害异己。时首辅周延儒政绩败坏，引起民愤，受各方指责。温体仁乘机排挤周延儒，于崇祯六年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1633)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">终于达到目的，取代了周延儒，出任首辅，温荣忱《辑里村志》载：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">马溪</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">马腰</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">世家沈氏有相国焉</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">指沈淮</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，浔溪世家有朱氏相国焉</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">指朱国祯</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，吾里之显亦家相也</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">指温体仁</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。按：相国即宰相，俗称阁老，三阁老各相距七里，故南浔民间有</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">七里三阁老</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">的传说。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　温体仁善察形辨色，迎合帝意，居位八年，为人外曲谨而内奸诈，同僚都敬而远之。帝渐悟其奸，温体仁亦有所觉察，遂于崇祯十年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1639)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">佯称因疾引退，试探帝意。自以为帝必加慰勉留任，及得旨，竟出乎意料放归故里，人心大快。崇祯十二年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1639)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卒，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">67</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁。崇祯末，福王立于南京，尚书顾锡畴乘机提议应考虑诸臣意见，福王准奏，削温体仁赠谥。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　按温体仁故里所产蚕丝，质量匀细洁白，用以织造，光彩夺目，人皆喜爱，乃以产地为名，称辑里丝，温体仁在帝后前又大肆宣扬，内宫及诸织造局，均选作上品丝织原料，声誉遂大扬。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．董</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">说</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1620—1686) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字若雨，号西庵，因居鹧鸪溪上故自称鹧鸪生，乌程南浔人。父董斯张</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1586--1628)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，号遐周，明万历廪贡生，笃好论诗，博学广思，著述有《吴兴备志》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">32</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷，《吴兴艺文补》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">70</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷，《弁山志辑》一卷，《广博物志》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">50</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷等。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　董说九岁丧父，事母至孝。自幼即承乃父好学家风，五岁即读四书五经，十岁能著文立说，十四岁补弟子员，旋食廪。弱冠能善观天象，通晓天文。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　明亡，时年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">25</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，即弃举业，不求功名，重民族气节，甘为遗民。并改姓林，取名蹇，字远游，号南村；蓄须，故亦称林胡子，又称槁木林。皈依苏州灵岩山寺，继起大师宏储名之曰元潜，字俟庵。隐居在浔南丰草庵</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">在鹧鸪溪上，为董说读书处，光绪中张钧衡在此筑适园</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，精研五经，尤专于易，方言、地志、星经、律法、释老之书，宗亲莫睹其面。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　清顺治十三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1656)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">秋，削发于灵岩山寺，法名南潜，字月涵</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">一作月岩</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，号补樵，一号枫巢，又有漏霜及宝云和尚等名，遂云游四方。返苏后，主持古尧峰宝云院，常往来于洞庭之西小湖及浔溪补船庵</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">又名漏霜庵，盖漏霜和尚即董说住所，在补船村，已早圯，今无考</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之间。康熙二十三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1684)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">奔母丧，葬毕归山后即不复来浔，尝寓吴之夕香庵，谢绝见客，潜心著作。康熙二十五年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1686)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">五月六日</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">园寂于夕香庵，时年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">67</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁。有六子，分别取名樵、牧、耒、舫、渔、村，弥留前戒诸子弃举业，以布衣终身。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　董说</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">25</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁后始重诗，以写其空坑崖海之思，有出世之慨。著《丰草庵诗集》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">11</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷、《宝云诗集》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷、《禅乐府》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">l</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷、《宝云诗甲编二卷乙存三卷》、《丙戌悲愤诗》一卷、《甲申乙酉诗歌》一卷及《南潜诗》一册等。董说博学多才，于学无所不窥，亦擅长草书。著述尚有《丰草庵杂著》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷、《丰草庵文集》三卷、《丰草庵书谱》，以及《七国考》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">14</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">分职官、食货、都邑、宫室、国名、群体、音乐、器服、杂记、丧制、兵制、刑法、灾异、琐征等</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">14</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">类，每类各分秦、齐、楚、赵、韩、魏、燕七国</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，《易发》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷、《易运》、《周易十八爻未济通论表》、《周易三十爻参天两地表》、《出震三易合表》、《洪范变》、《周礼纬》、卷、《运气定论》一卷，《左传提》一卷、《律吕发》一卷、《六书发》、《史记脉》、《二代文献》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">即《夏殷文献》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">、《浔书》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">据董说《浔书序》云：凡生于斯，长于斯，读书于斯，得四十四人而集其文谓之</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">浔书</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，《天象编年》、《岁差考》等。此外尚有《林胡子野语》四卷、《楝花矶随笔》一卷、《灵岩首座寮语录》二卷、《灵岩余录》、《补船长语》八卷、《宝云语录》二卷、《宝云别录》四卷、《宝云杂著》一卷、《西游补》等等。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　《周志》据《诗萃》云：董说名著</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">复社</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">为明末一部分江南士大夫主张改良政治，谋求挽救明王朝的统治，太仓人张溥和张采等合并江南的若干文社，组成团体，称为</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">复社</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">崇祯六年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1633)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">在苏州虎丘举行大会。但据沈登瀛考证：按吴曾羽《复社姓氏录》及陆世仪《复社纪略》皆无董说名，况</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">复社</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">盛于崇祯二至三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1629—1630)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，不久即构祸而辍，董说年尚少，故《诗萃》所谓董说名著</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">复社</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之说，恐非确实。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> <span></span></font></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">6</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．刘桐</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1759—1803) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">刘桐字舜挥，号疏雨，清乌程南浔人。例贡生，候选州同。祖居东大街德懋弄口，雄于资而多家累，未及三十即廪举业，远游楚。生平好聚书，为清乾嘉间南浔有名的藏书家。《汪志》介绍说：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">锐志聚书，积至十余万卷，凡宋椠及精写本。不惜兼金罗致，插架之富，白天一阁，瓶花斋外，莫之及也</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。刘疏雨择其所居东厢为藏书处。取名</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">眠琴山馆</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　刘桐既爱好聚书，也好与喜书者交往，对来访或求阅者，无不乐于接待，使满意而归，人皆感之。名家如张鉴、范锴、计深、钱大昕、蒋履泰、施国祁、严可均、杨凤苞、邢典等，均为其座上客。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　嘉庆二十五年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1820)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，张鉴、范锴、计深、蒋履泰为刘桐编《眠琴山馆藏书目》。张在序中说：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">乾隆壬子癸丑间</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1792--1793)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，疏雨既藏书自任，吾湖因多贾客，织里一乡居者皆以佣书为业出则扁舟孤棹，举凡平江远近数百里之间，简籍不胫而走。盖自元时至今，凡四百载，上至部门三下迨海舶，苟得一善本，辄蛛丝马迹，缘沿而购取之</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。又说：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">东南贮藏之家与汲古之士，如钱塘何梦华，嘉兴鲍绿饮，接踵而至，所得之书益精且美。其时又适值卢氏抱经堂，吴氏瓶花斋校精本散出四方，于是疏雨所收之富又越从前数倍</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。从而可知，刘桐通过各种渠道，收买善本和精钞本，抢救了古籍的散佚。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> <br>
</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　钱大昕曾去眠琴山馆阅书，在他的《竹汀日记》中说：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">过南浔镇晤刘疏雨，观所藏书有宋椠《张九成孟子解》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">29</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">又</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">徐天麒《两汉会要》，岳珂《愧郯录》，皆宋椠，甚精。胡安国《春秋传》亦宋椠，传文比经低一格，卷未有元至正三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1347)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">后丁丑秋</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，陈留边子昂手整于姑苏邓明仲家塾，墨迹如新。又元椠有《周礼义疏》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷。每卷首题吴兴后学陈友仁君复编，其第</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷则俞延椿《周礼复古编》也。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">刘疏雨还收藏有历史价值的稀有钞本，如《皇元圣武亲征录》、《中兴御侮录》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">以上无撰写人</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，《襄阳守城录》赵万年撰，宋王象之《舆地纪胜》，汲古阁写本《滏水集说》。尚有明黄忠烈</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">武英殿大学士黄道周</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">夫人蔡玉卿手写楷书《孝经》卷，系绢本，高一尺，长一丈五尺二寸五分。此外如刘一止的《苕溪集》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">55</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷，无序跋，系钞本；《圣宋名贤</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">500</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">家播芳大全文萃》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">100</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷，瞿山精舍叶菜子实编，富学堂魏齐贤仲贤校正等，亦甚可贵。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　刘桐聚书志未竟，于嘉庆八年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1803)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之秋病逝，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">45</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁。遗著有《楚游草》、《楚游续草》、《昕雨轩集》。刘桐死后，子刘英年幼，妻又不善治理。这些宝贵藏书部分为陆心源廉价收买，成为丽宋楼插架，其余大多散佚，友好深为惋惜。严可均为《刘小梦忆书图》题跋云：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">君家疏雨我好友，积书之癖与我同，别来江干亭边树，终古山阳笛里风。有人微名都折福，世界家举总成空，只今说着眠琴馆，卅六年一梦中</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。张鉴曾课诵其家十余载，深有感触，叹曰：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">书之聚散，古人以比云烟过眼，本无足异。然聚书之速，散之尤速，未有过我友疏雨者，此可慨也。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．　顾福昌</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1796--1868) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字成之，号春池，清乌程南浔人，国学生，因排行第六，创业后，大家称他顾六公公。童年家贫，母早卒，弃学从商，初在镇上摆布摊，后至震泽开小布店，兼营蚕丝。妻朱氏照顾老父，浔震相距</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">里，他每天朝出晚归，徒步往还，寒暑无间断，秉性勤俭至孝。父病卒后，结束布店，全力在南浔经营辑里丝，开设顾丰盛丝行。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　清道光初，顾福昌去上海，当时上海尚未开商埠，但已有英美商人前来通商，急觅经纪人。顾福昌机敏好学，与洋人往来，渐能通译外语，遂成为上海早期的丝通事，经理洋务。他在四马路开设顾丰盛丝号，后改顾寿泰丝号，与南浔顾丰盛丝行相呼应。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">1843</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年上海辟为通商口岸，辑里丝直接从上海出口，顾福昌既是丝通事，周旋在洋商之间，对丝市行情信息灵通。他又是顾丰盛丝号的老板，更是得心应手，发了大财，为南浔丝商中发迹最早的一家。当时南浔丝行中出名的有四家，即顾福昌的顾丰盛，朱兆传的朱宏茂，邱仙槎的邱启昌，刘镛的刘正茂，故丝业界流传着</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">顾六公公朱九伯，仙槎二叔伢三哥</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">的顺口溜</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">伢南浔士音</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">nga</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，即我们，三哥指刘三东家刘镛</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> <br>
</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　顾福昌经营蚕丝致富后，买进了当时上海滩上唯一的外洋轮船码头</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">——</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">金利源码头，并大造堆栈，与洋商结纳，独占了上海进出口货物装卸和打包的业务。因管理有方，深得洋商信任，被提升为怡和洋行买办，怡和打包公司经理。他在上海北苏州河路，南浔南西街华家弄北首，南西街泰安桥堍陶家弄西及西大街竹行弄东等处建有大住宅，南浔人称顾家为顾丰盛，为南浔富豪中</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">四象</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之一。同治七年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1863)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">病卒于上海，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">73</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁。他因对英美商务有贡献，故徐有珂的《赠中仪大夫顾君暨配朱淑人墓志铭》中说：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">其卒也，花旗国领事馆命挂半旗，此为外国隆礼。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”<br>
</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　顾福昌有三个儿子，长子名寿松字容斋，次子名寿藏字子嘉，三子名寿朋字颂三，都是有名的古物、金石、书画收藏家，杭州邹适、卢寿祺为寿松编《两颇斋藏器目》。为寿藏编《石林山房彝器文字目》，为文物考古与史学家所推重。顾氏三兄弟继承父业，经营蚕丝，以顾寿藏最有声望，曾任上海丝业公所董事长，为南浔丝业界筹办丝业恤嫠会于南浔丝业公所内，后因囤丝亏损，卖去上海金利源码头、古藏器和南浔西华家弄北首的大住宅。故</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">四象</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">中以顾家衰落较早，其曾孙顾乾麟</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">又名顾怡康</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">抗日战争前后在上海和香港重振了顾氏家业。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">．　</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">汪曰桢</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1812--1882)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">号谢城，又号薪甫，清乌程南浔人。父汪延泽，字润之，工诗有令名。母赵蔡，出名门，博通经史，淬志教子。汪曰桢得力母教，又博览群书，故学有根源。咸丰二年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1832)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">举人，旋补会稽教谕，官俸收入，半供刻书费用，有《荔墙丛刻》十六集行世。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　汪曰桢精史学、算术、天文、历法，长于推步勾股之学，冈历术纠纷，乃上起西周共和元年，下迄明末，各以当时用术，步其朔润，略如万年历的格式，成《二十四史月日考》五十三卷</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">《周志</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">．</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">汪曰桢传》作《历代长术》五十三卷</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，继简为《历代长术辑要》十卷，与所著《古今推步诸术考》二卷附于后，相为发明，津逮后学。还潜心于地方志，修《南浔镇志》四十卷</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">简称《汪志》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，体例谨严，尤为方志学家推重。他还曾参与修《乌程县志》、《湖州府志》。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　汪曰桢尚撰有《莲漪草堂文钞》八卷，《四声切韵表补正》五卷，《玉鉴堂诗存》二卷，《古文》二卷，《骈文》二卷，《荔墙词》一卷，《方甲》一卷，《温热经纬评》五卷，《湖雅》四卷，《湖蚕述》四卷等。汪精通医理，文墨不废，耄而益勤。太平天国军退出浙江后，他向左宗棠上陈善后条程。左宗棠重其才，有</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">晶端学邃，识仪超群</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之褒，委他襄办军务，坚辞不就。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">光绪八年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1882)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卒，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">7l</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁，无嗣。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">9</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．张颂贤</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1817—1892) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字竹斋，清乌程南浔人，祖籍徽州休宁，曾祖张振先于康熙年间始迁南浔。祖张秀升，父张维岳，勤于商，在南浔开小酱盐店</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">?</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">维岳有二子，颂贤为其次，娶同里吴处士鲲长女为妻，生二子，长子张宝庆、字质甫，孙张钧衡；次子张宝善，字定甫，孙七，依次为张弁群、张静江、张澹如、张墨耕、张让之、张久香和张镜芙。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　张颂贤善经营，稍积资金，遂从事丝业。道光二十二年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1842)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，鸦片战争失败，五口通商，上海于</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">1843</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年辟为通商口岸，南浔辑里丝畅销外洋。张颂贤看准时机，在南浔丝行埭和上海增泰丝栈分设张恒和丝行与丝号，聘请得力丝通事，全力经营辑里丝出口业务，成为巨富，在南浔东吊桥外建大住宅，宅后原</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">东墅</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">古园废址上建</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">东园</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，俗名张家花园。本地人以恒和丝行出名，故称张家为张恒和。分家后，张质甫迁居南西街华家弄口，购进原顾丰盛大住宅，经扩建后称南恒和，立堂名懿德；张定甫仍住老宅，扩建新厦，称东恒和，立堂名尊德。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　张颂贤营丝发家后，又着眼于盐务。太平天国时期</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1851—1864)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，浙江沿海动乱不定，盐官逃跑，私盐充斥，盐商所持食盐引票失去统销保障，纷纷抛售，引票价值惨跌。按清制盐以引计，每引若干斤，已纳税的称引盐，经营引盐的商人，国家给与引商运销引盐的票据，称引票，引商划定销售的地区范围，称为引岸，故有</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">专商引岸</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之名，为抗日战争前对食盐有高度垄断性的专卖制度。张颂贤廉价购进杭州大盐商朱恒源的十万引票，又把朱恒源过户为张恒源，其他盐商有转让引票的，亦悉数收并，张家遂成为引商大户。同治三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1864)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，太平天国军退出浙江，盐区重新设官统制，引票价格猛涨十倍，骤然扩大了张家的财富。张颂贤对整顿盐务有一手策略，他约诸盐商收余姚岱山盐民的私盐轻课减价，惠及盐民，加强缉查，断绝了私盐的来路，达到官商两利。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">他看到日本蚕丝在国际市场竞争剧烈，丝价又操在外商之手，预感辑里丝外销好景不长，因而弃丝专营盐务。在上海九江路大庆里设总管理处，称恒源总账房，由外甥李惟奎字联仙任总经理，原恒和丝行账房林梅生为协理，又得姻亲周湘龄的襄助，除占有浙西大部分引盐权外，还占有苏五属</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">苏州、常州、无锡、镇江、太仓</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">等府属引盐权的大部分。张家有</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">多万引票，每引</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">381</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">斤，单是苏五属年销量在</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">30YY</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">担以上。在浙北、皖南、苏南的部分大城镇设盐公堂，为统销引盐的基层机构，经营批发业务，兼有查辑和扣押私贩之权，故名</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">公堂</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。因赢利较丰，成为张家的摇钿树。张家经营的是浙盐，刘家经营的是淮盐，同为盐业界巨头。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　张颂贤既然有盐，不仅垄断了引岸范围内的食盐运销，也垄断了腌腊业和酱业的用盐，还动脑筋在本地搞起了盐对食品的加工利用。在南浔独资或合资开办了张恒泰、张恒昌、张元泰、张启泰、张义隆等酱园，在外地还设分店，经营造酱，做酱油、辣酱、酱菜和腐乳等，还扩展到腌腊加工业务，几乎垄断了南浔镇周围方圆</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">50</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">里内各乡镇的食盐和酱制品等的批发和销售。此外张颂贤在马家港河东建宗祠，在徽州、常熟、南浔等地购置庄田，赡养和奖恤族人。开典当、钱庄、办通运公司、投资银行，经营房地产等等，财源滚滚，家大业大，至光绪中，张家已成为南浔富豪中的</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">四象</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之一，实力仅次于</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">四象</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之首的刘家。张颂贤于光绪十八年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1812)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">病卒，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">76</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁，恩封资政大夫，户部贵州司郎中。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．刘镛</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(182</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卜</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">1899) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字贯经，清乌程南浔人，祖籍上虞，高祖刘尚贤于清康熙初迁居南浔，曾祖刘湛恩、祖刘元吉，父刘焕章，有三子，长名刘铉，家原住南东街莲家弄口，为大房；次名刘锵，家原住通津桥南堍东首，称刘二房。刘镛排行第三，发迹后人称他为刘三东家。相传祖上业铜匠，后开铜匠铺于丝行埭，前刘氏家庙神龛中供小铜匠担一副借以教育子孙，饮水思源，创业维艰。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　刘镛少年时南浔辑里丝畅销，诸父辈都帮人从事丝业，遂弃学去本镇蒋元春绵绸店当学徒，年余，闻其师岁人仅百缗，每缗为制钱一千文，认为业此难于生财发家，遂脱离绵绸店，到邱启昌丝行当夥计，四年尽通丝行中的奥秘。适值鸦片战争失败，上海辟为商埠，洋人在上海大购湖丝，南浔辑里丝出口剧增，年在八九万包。刘镛抓住时机，与邢赓星合夥开设正茂丝行，经营有方，遂获大利，不数年已俨然成为阔老板。他省悟到，若要发大财，必须直接与洋人贸易，免受中间剥削；又必须独资经营，利润独占，且不受干扰。乃与邢赓星拆伙，独资在上海阜安里设刘贯记丝号，与洋商直接贸易，出口为主。在南浔改设刘振茂丝行，主坐收加工，转运上海。刘镛得心应手，同治初年已殖财白银数十万两。他在经营蚕丝出口贸易中，深感丝价为洋人操纵，没有保障，乃改营盐务，设扬州盐场，成为淮盐有实力的引商。他兼并土地，置庄田，在上海、汉口、青岛等开放口岸，开发房地产，以经营典当，开钱庄，投资银行，涉足金融市场，从各种渠道，扩大其资产。至光绪中，其财富居南浔</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">四象</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之首。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　刘镛深感列祖以来，包括自己在内，缺少文化，虽有财，但无禄，不上门第，故亟力教子读书，应试科举，盼子成龙，以求荣宗耀祖。他有四个儿子，长子刘安澜，字紫回，同治</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">11</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1872)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">秀才，附贡生，为大房，立堂名尊德，建宅于白鹇兜，名尊德里。刘安澜</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">29</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁就病卒，无子，以刘锦藻的长子刘承干继承。次子刘安江，又名锦藻，字徵如，光绪二十年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1894)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">进士，立堂名贻德，住宅在南西街新开河口。三子刘安注，字梯青，光绪十九年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1893)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">秀才，立堂名崇德，住宅在南东街花园弄口。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　四子刘安溥，字湖涵，立堂名景德，住宅在南东街凤凰桥南首。刘镛冈儿子刘锦藻进士及弟，恩封通奉大夫。他为光耀门第，把女儿嫁给一晶大学士徐都字颂阁的儿子为妻，在政治上也有了靠山。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　刘镛善于处世，既富冠乡里，又上了门第，后半世就行善积德，凡义塾、书院、育婴堂等义举，无不捐资提倡。同治八年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1869)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，浙江大水，湖州受灾尤重，米价飞涨。灾民乞食。刘镛筹金数万，雇轮船向芜湖购米万石，赈济平粜，人心大定。他还教育子孙要关心族人，亲善乡邻，热心社会公益。他的事迹，受到清廷褒奖，圣旨恩准在家庙中建积善牌坊，赐</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">乐善好施</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">题词。他教育子孙，要团结亲族，共振刘氏家业，并置庄田，扶助贫困族人，故又获钦赐</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">承先睦族</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">九龙金匾。刘镛于光绪</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">25</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1899)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">病卒，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">74</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">11</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．庞云镨</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1833—1889) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">字芸皋，清乌程南浔人。原籍绍兴，祖庞夷简迁居南浔。父庞听泉，在湖南历任师爷、幕僚，庞云镨在浔读书侍奉母亲，</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">15</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁去镇上陈裕昌丝行当学徒，满师后已通晓蚕丝经营之道，以及晶评丝质优劣的技术。母卒，娶江苏震泽刘处士方舟的次女为妻，生三子，长名庞景麟，早夭；次为庞元济字莱臣，三为庞元澄字青城。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">咸丰十一年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1861)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，太平天国军进驻南浔，庞云镨奉父命避居上海，从事丝业，不数月父卒，目南浔料理父丧，遂不复去上海。他精于蚕丝经营，时洋商在上海大量收购辑里丝，价格上扬，庞云镨看准时机，但资金短缺，乃与镇人张氏</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">张源泰丝行主人</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">蒋氏</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">蒋元春丝行主人</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">合伙，在丝行埭开设丝行，发了财。由于庞云错独揽大权，致使合资者不满，并忌其才，以拆伙为由施加压力，他就独资经营，在上海泰康里设庞怡泰丝号，为行庄，专与洋商搞出口贸易。在南浔丝行埭设庞怡泰丝行，为坐庄，收购转运。并亲自在上海与外商打交道，探询国际丝市动态和丝价起伏，根据上海丝市的盈虚，嘱使南浔坐庄进退。冈信息灵通，经营有魄力，不数年家产暴发，成为财主。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　庞云镨在经营蚕丝中，结识了杭州胡庆余堂国药店老板胡雪岩，即胡光墉，成为莫逆之交。胡雪岩的后台是左宗棠，是左宗棠麾下的一员得力助手，人称他为</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">红顶商人</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，即带官帽的做生意人。他有雄心囤积蚕丝，与洋商竞争，约庞云镨合作，大量收购湖丝。庞云销，只答应代为收购，不介入合资。后来胡雪岩冈囤丝受到丝货壅滞，洋商抑价的影响，几至破产，而庞云镨只是转手代购，毫无经济损失，却从中捞到一笔大利。有胡雪岩的前车之鉴，庞云镨从此不再经营蚕丝，并告诫他的儿子说：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">白老虎可怕，莫再经营蚕丝</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，他把蚕丝比作</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">白老虎</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。他深感自己少文，虽然有钱，却无门第，要儿子努力读书，望子成龙，庞元济与庞元澄先后于光绪六年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1880)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">及二十一年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1895)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">考中了秀才。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　庞云镨在上海经营蚕丝与洋商周旋中，结识了一些外商朋友，其中有贩卖军火的，庞认为这是极好的生财之道。时左宗棠西征新疆，委派胡雪岩在上海办采运局务，急需新式武器，胡雪岩就委托庞云镨与洋商接洽，达成军火交易，转运给左宗棠，既完成了胡雪岩的受命任务，为左宗棠西征新疆，剿平阿古柏勾结回民叛徒白彦虎的作乱出了大力，又获得了暴利，进一步扩大了庞云镨的财富，成为南浔</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">四象</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之一。他在东大街建大住宅，前临街，后沿栲栳湾，里人称庞家为庞怡泰。庞云镨与洋商结纳，大做军火生意，为免受非议，以他儿子庞元济的名义，对大清王朝捐献了十万两纹银，所谓赈捐豫直灾情报效，由李鸿章奏奖。光绪十七年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1891)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">得慈禧太后旨恩赏庞元济举人，特赏庞云镨一品封典，候补四品京堂。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　庞云镨还仿胡雪岩的胡庆余堂，在南浔住宅门埭开设规模较大的庞滋德国药店，建有药栈和制药工场，供应饮片和成药，并有名医坐堂处方，业务很广，誉满周围乡镇。又冈与张颂贤有姻亲关系，盐有保证，在镇北开设庞怡泰酱园，附有酿造和加工作场，在南栅还有分店，为南浔酱园中很有经济实力的一家。为赡养族人，在东吊桥外建宗祠和义庄。光绪十五年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1889)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">病卒，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">57</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁。恩赠荣禄大夫，光禄大夫，刑部江西司郎中。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">．刘锦藻</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1862-1934) </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">原名刘安江，字徵如，吴兴南浔人。父刘镛，虽然有钱但自感少文无门第，于是力促儿辈努力读书，盼子成龙。清光绪元年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">土</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">875)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">藻中秀才，十四年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1888)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">中举人，二十年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1891)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">进京赶考，与南通的张謇同榜甲午科进士及第，并一起参加了殿试。张謇中了状元，刘锦藻则为两榜进士。他与张謇从文墨之交，成为挚友。时有萧山汤寿潜，光绪十八年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1-892)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">进士，与张謇同为康有为、梁启超、谭嗣同等创设的</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">强学会</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">会员，交往密切，经张謇的介绍，刘锦藻与汤寿潜也交上了朋友，从此与南浔结下了缘。光绪二十四年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1898)“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">戊戌变法</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">即所谓百日维新</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">失败，慈禧太后临朝专政，清查</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">强学会</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，汤寿潜从北京潜回杭州。适清废科举，刘锦藻倡议浔溪书院，常课外，并授经史、时务、策论，推举汤寿潜来南浔主讲新课，出任浔溪书院山长</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">相当于院长</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">崇尚新学。在刘锦藻的引荐下，汤寿潜也结识了庞莱臣、周湘龄、蒋汝藻、张钧衡等镇绅。光绪三十一年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1905)7</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">月，为抵制英美商向清政府以铁路借款为诱饵，企图掠夺苏杭甬铁路与浙赣铁路之权，汤寿潜与刘锦藻约浙江绅商在上海集议，拒绝英美借款，决定在浙江自造铁路，创办浙江铁路公司。举汤寿潜和刘锦藻为正副总经理，庞莱臣、周湘龄、蒋汝藻、张钧衡等当选为董事，并投了资。以刘锦藻为首的南浔财团，成了浙江铁路公司的支柱，积极参予保路运动。光绪三十三年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1907)11</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">月，为抵制外国银行侵占金融市场和开发地方经济，刘锦藻与汤寿潜倡议浙江铁路公司集资</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">100</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">万元，在杭州创办浙江兴业银行，为浙江第一家商业银行，发行钞票，流通市场，刘锦藻、庞莱臣、周湘龄、张钧衡都投了资。刘锦藻还参与倡议在杭州举办高等工业学堂，设建筑与机械两科，培养工业技术人才。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　刘锦藻承父业，经营淮盐，设扬州盐场，为淮盐的大盐商。在通州设垦牧公司，在上海设大达轮船公司和码头，还经营房地产，扬州设有经租帐房，杭州、莫干山均有别墅。并广开当铺，在南浔投资浔震电灯公司，开设刘振茂绸缎局。他关心社会慈善事业，光绪二十一年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1895)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，美国南监理会教士韩明德</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">美国人</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">在湖州海岛围地建教堂</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">海岛堂</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">侵占尊经阁、颜鲁公祠，曹孝子祠等房地</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">50</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">余亩，湖郡邑绅累经交涉无效，后诉讼上达京师总理衙门，均以涉外关系，未获结果。刘锦藻</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">与韩教士曾有交往，约张弁群同访，据理洽谈，退地问题获得解决。他在南浔创建义仓俗称积谷仓，贮备稻谷，救济贫民。特别在兴学方面，对地方曾作了贡献。民国</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1916)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，他在积谷仓内创建孺嫠小学，为一所正规的私立初级小学，供孤苦儿童免费入学。民国</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">18</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1929)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，他把孺嫠小学归并南浔中学，开办南浔中学附属小学，还捐款</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">5000</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">元作为基金。他在刘氏义庄置庄田，设家塾，供本族贫寒子弟免费入学。又从义庄收益中提成作为兴学经费，制订了切实的兴学办法：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">一</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">津贴学费方面；凡在义庄所设两等小学就读的，其学膳费家庭负担确实困难的全免。有愿人其它学校读书无力负担者，凡人初小每年支钱</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，高小</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">16</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，中学</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">40</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">二</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">升学送川资方面：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　凡高等小学毕业送考外地中学的支钱</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；中学毕业送考高等学堂的支钱</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；省校毕业送考京师大学堂的支钱</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">30</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；官费出洋留学，去东洋的支钱</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">40</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，去西洋的加倍支付。凡留学回国，进京应试的支钱</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">40</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；送考海陆军及师范实业的均按比例。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> (</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">三</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">奖赠毕业方面：高等小学</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　毕业最优等的奖赠</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">12</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，优等、中等</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；初等实业同。中学堂毕业最优等及优等的</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，中等</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">15</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；初级师范、中等实业同。高等学堂毕业最优等、优等、中等</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">30</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文。大学堂毕业分科列最优等者</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">80</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，优等</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">60</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，中等</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">50</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；选科最优等者</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">60</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文，优等、中等</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">50</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">千文；海陆军及留学毕业赴京考取者，仿上例议赠。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">以上系按光绪二十一年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1895)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">生活标准拟定</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><br>
<br>
</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">　　</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">南浔西郊有古</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">挂瓢池</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，光绪十一年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1885)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，刘锦藻在池畔筑屋以厝伯兄刘安渊</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">紫回</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">之柩，后以挂瓢池改建为园林。以莲池为中心，沿池补栽花木，点缀假山、曲桥，布置亭榭楼阁，名</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">小莲庄</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。民国</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">13</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1924)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">又扩建内园，凿池栽芰，叠石成山，松径一湾，枫林四匝，拾级登山，颇有杜牧《山行》诗意。据刘锦藻《小莲庄记略》说：</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">因赵雪松</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">孟颊</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">有莲花庄，额之曰小莲庄</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">。并在西侧建义庄曰刘氏家庙。现小莲庄已列为省重点文物保护单位。光绪二十七年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1901)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">，刘锦藻向清廷出资助赈陕西灾难，依例授候补四品京堂。同年写成《续皇朝文献通考》</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">400</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">卷进呈，赏内阁侍读学士衔。后来上海商务印书馆汇印《九通》时，将《续皇朝文献通考》增人，成为《十通》。其著述尚有《南浔备志》三卷，《坚匏庵诗文钞》四卷，《杂著》二卷，《律赋》一卷，《楹联》一卷等。刘锦藻于民国</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">23</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">(1934)</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">病逝上海寓所，终年</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">73</font></span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:宋体;">岁